//      Conditional statements ie, control instructions.

/*
There is four types-
1. dicision control instruction-->
                 if
                 nested if
                 if else
                 nested if else
                 if elseif ladder
                 conditional operator (?:)(ternary operator).

2. iterative(repeatative) control instruction--> (Loops)
                 while
                 do while
                 for

3. switch case control instruction-->(syntex)
        switch(expression)
        {
            case constant:code;break;
            case constant:code;break;
            case constant:code;break;
            default:code;
        }
4. goto control instruction-->
*/


/*  
iterative(repeatative) control instructons(Loops)
         while(T/F)--(entry control)
         do while--(exit contrl)
         for--(initialization;condition;updation )
         for--(expression-1;expression-2;expression-3)

for( ; ; ) => for loop may be empty , then called infinite loop, but
              while loop should never be empty.         
*/


/*    break;
     the keyword break can be used only in loop body or in switch body.
     the purpose of break is to terminate the loop's excution immediatly.
*/


/*
switch case control instruction-->(syntex)

        switch(expression)
        {
            case constant:code;break;
            case constant:code;break;
            case constant:code;break;
            default:code;
        }

Note:
1-
 switch(expression) ye expression if else aur loops me T/F ki tarah evaluate 
hota hain but switch k expression me T/F ki tarah nhi balki simply result ki tarah
hoga aur ye result constant k equal hoga aur default tb chalega jb koi bhi case 
expression k result se satisfied nhi hoga aur yh expression constant ya variable
bhi ho sakta hain.
2-
 case ke aage variable ya expresion nhi likh saktey, sirf constant likh saktey hai
aur constant may be integer or character but not real number means not point value.
3- 
case ko kisi bhi order me likh saktey hain but ydi default ko bich me likhtey 
hain to default k bad bhi break; keyword lagana padega eshliye default ko last me 
likhtey hain. waise hume serial nu. se likhne ka aadat dalna chahiye.
*/
